{"tid":1293554,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌現場既人, 留係現場既人請你地入一入嚟, 依家要諗下文宣點做","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:24:01.000Z","uid":69291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1730b7ff1ccf0f1d5858875cf6ba2d8c95efc55c","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"屌現場唔走既人<br />\n我明白你地好擔心現場既人<br />\n唔希望任何人被補<br />\n因為再有一個人畀人拉都係太多<br />\n唔想見到佢地畀人打, 流血, 受傷<br />\n但請你地收一收口, 唔好人身攻擊<br />\n成件事佢地係處於被動<br />\n好多人到依家都唔走係因為現場有人未走<br />\n係想全部人都走得到<br />\n咁點解唔散呀？<br />\n有夢遊過都知, 你落單就出事<br />\n現場既人就係怕落單仲危險<br />\n<br />\n留係現場既人<br />\n請你地明白連登呢到好多人都好擔心你<br />\n我地唔想失去任何一個<br />\n因為全部都係自己兄弟<br />\n如果因為你地一個未走<br />\n就有多一個人會想陪你, 為咗保護你而一齊唔走<br />\n到最後好多人就繼續留係現場<br />\n留絕對無問題, 但請考慮下現場環境<br />\n認真諗一諗個形勢<br />\n唔好為一時之氣就畀狗有機會入<br />\n<br />\n最後, 希望所有人可以將個焦點放係彌敦道包抄個到<br />\n明明所有人都退緊<br />\n但啲狗一再進逼, 繼而將所有人包起彌敦道唔放人<br />\n呢個係一個好危險既舉動<br />\n驚慌既人群係有好大機會發生人踩人既慘劇<br />\n佢地既策略係絕對有問題, <br />\n希望文宣組, 所有巴絲將個焦點放係呢個咁危險既決策上面<br />\n<br />\n肯出嚟既都係戰友,<br />\n 不分化、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n唔係現場既人, 請集中思考點幫現場既人士<br />\n係現場既人, 請盡力留意情勢, be water"},{"pid":"ae785417f2ffe02d696d1fb240b1dae48a633caa","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dd750da856a780fb29d93474906314b1eb918f","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606f968a69447c4911545b63845dd04d64536745","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e321ca8ce1ca036f60976d26121e8f88816d69a7","tid":1293554,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/deadline.hongkong/videos/2509009319130549/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdeadline.hongkong%2Fvideos%2F2509009319130549%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=aee94b74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/deadline.hongkong/videos/2509009319130549/</a><br />\n<br />\n狗自己講唔比人走"},{"pid":"67cf1c1cd20d537ad97704ff0f70f544e4650a8b","tid":1293554,"uid":275607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5f2cf18063d387de7211ddb66d4de00caeee63","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ffae7d2437654e34cdc640d7eaa1fda8d403d6","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49f7e73ff970af320584f502d674448168a79b4","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb00d3f2921a39b35533faa89d28fa9a0b18325d","tid":1293554,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5c554aaf3c7ed09a1134619986e3e19d4039bc","tid":1293554,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"前線發夢傾好要左一齊走，就唔好自己留！！ 拉人走既一定要拉實D,一定要拉走到！！"}]}